07:13.460 --> 07:15.370
Settle the case.

07:15.420 --> 07:18.560
A big lump of cash may chase her away.

07:18.810 --> 07:20.760
I'm not settling.

07:20.800 --> 07:23.280
This is my company we're talking about.

07:23.320 --> 07:25.380
Is it?

07:27.650 --> 07:30.380
settle the case, walt.

07:33.320 --> 07:39.440
I remember the very day I brought claire in
to meet then ceo alan dupree for his approval.

07:39.480 --> 07:43.390
Mind you, these were the days
when I still needed approval.

07:44.510 --> 07:47.790
claire comes in and dazzles.

07:47.840 --> 07:49.880
It was the best
interview I've ever seen.

07:49.920 --> 07:52.950
But I'll never forget what the
old bastard said after she left.

07:52.990 --> 07:57.160
He turned to me and said,
"walt, she's a woman."

07:57.170 --> 08:01.730
I said, "shit, alan, is
that what they call it?"

08:02.230 --> 08:07.960
and I told him, "alan, i guarantee, if
we make her an offer today, in 20 years,

08:08.000 --> 08:11.060
we'll be taking marching
orders from her."

