And here we are, claire, 20 years later.

08:14.550 --> 08:19.810
Alan dupree is living off a golden parachute
in scottsdale, and you're still flying high.

08:19.820 --> 08:22.940
To claire.

08:25.740 --> 08:28.480
well, I just want to thank
everybody for coming out tonight.

08:28.540 --> 08:33.789
I love this company, and, uh,
I've loved my last 20 years,

08:33.799 --> 08:36.830
and I'm looking forward to another 20.

08:37.299 --> 08:40.679
We know that I'm only here
because of your belief in me, walt,

08:40.720 --> 08:44.169
and, uh, I think all of us know that.

08:44.210 --> 08:48.130
