09:22.090 --> 09:24.600
Thanks for coming, dad.

09:28.200 --> 09:30.110
At least he showed. That says something.

09:30.120 --> 09:33.450
Really? What's that?

09:33.690 --> 09:36.440
- You mind a bit of business?
- Please.

09:37.480 --> 09:40.950
About this patty hewes case--
I think it's time to settle.

09:40.960 --> 09:44.630
I don't understand. The stocks are
recovering. Her case has no merit.

09:44.640 --> 09:48.140
Ah, just settle it. You can
go as high as 50 million.

09:48.150 --> 09:50.690
But you said there was going
to be an influx of capital.

09:50.720 --> 09:51.910
There's no reason why
the company or your...

09:51.960 --> 09:56.010
Claire, I've made my decision.

10:00.900 --> 10:03.640
Man's inconsolable loneliness.

10:03.680 --> 10:07.440
Bereft. Forsaken. Wretched.

10:07.450 --> 10:10.880
