10:19.950 --> 10:21.890
Hey, did you hear from any colleges yet?

10:21.930 --> 10:24.420
Nope, not yet.

10:24.430 --> 10:27.060
Do you want to hit up
delaney's party tonight?

10:27.080 --> 10:28.890
