19:01.940 --> 19:05.800
Imagine my surprise when i picked it
up and there was a man on the line.

19:06.110 --> 19:08.870
It's probably the new guy she's seeing.

19:08.910 --> 19:11.300
Some real estate douche bag.

19:11.330 --> 19:14.440
Keeps threatening me
about pam's alimony.

19:15.720 --> 19:18.630
I spoke to pam.

19:19.280 --> 19:22.100
